<emphasis bold="true" box="[602,717,1904,1925]" pageId="22" pageNumber="223">comb. nov.</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="22.[151,1436,1971,2031]" lastBlockId="23.[151,1437,151,392]" lastPageId="23" lastPageNumber="224" pageId="22" pageNumber="223">Notes on the paratype; thorax dark emerald green, scutellar disc with slightly more bluish reflections. Basal and second tarsomeres clear yellow, others darkened but not black just darker yellow. Lunule with ground colour orange-brown, covered with silver pollinosity, arista short plumose, plumes approximately 2.5x width of arista. Wings slightly yellowish, calypteres and their fringes entirely white.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="23" pageNumber="224" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="23.[151,1437,151,392]" pageId="23" pageNumber="224">
<materialsCitation ID-GBIF-Occurrence="1423743138" collectingDate="1959-03-01" collectingDateMax="1959-03-20" collectingDateMin="1959-03-01" country="Tanzania" county="Marangu" latitude="-3.2833333" location="This" longLatPrecision="1307" longitude="37.516666" municipality="Morge" pageId="23" pageNumber="224" specimenCount="1">
<location LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:03A7DC54FFB1BB20FF6BF8CBFF01FE1A:8ED13B99FFB0BB20FF3BFF3DFF04FF6A" box="[199,249,223,248]" country="Tanzania" county="Marangu" latitude="-3.2833333" longLatPrecision="1307" longitude="37.516666" municipality="Morge" name="This" pageId="23" pageNumber="224">This</location>
species was also described by 
<bibRefCitation author="Morge" box="[599,756,224,248]" pageId="23" pageNumber="224" refString="Morge, G. (1980) Lonchaeidae (Diptera) aus Afrika sudlich der Sahara mit Beschreibung von drei neuen Arten. Beitrage zur Entomologie, 30, 315 - 332." type="journal article" year="1980">
<collectingMunicipality box="[599,673,224,248]" pageId="23" pageNumber="224">Morge</collectingMunicipality>
(1980)
</bibRefCitation>
on the basis of female specimens collected in 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1282,1429,223,248]" pageId="23" pageNumber="224">
<collectingCountry box="[1282,1429,223,248]" name="Tanzania" pageId="23" pageNumber="224">TANZANIA</collectingCountry>
</emphasis>
, 
<collectingCounty box="[151,255,261,285]" pageId="23" pageNumber="224">Marangu</collectingCounty>
, (
<geoCoordinate box="[277,371,260,284]" direction="south" orientation="latitude" pageId="23" pageNumber="224" precision="925" value="-3.2833333">3° 17' S</geoCoordinate>
. 
<geoCoordinate box="[384,494,260,284]" direction="east" orientation="longitude" pageId="23" pageNumber="224" precision="925" value="37.516666">37° 31' E</geoCoordinate>
.) 
<date box="[516,666,260,285]" pageId="23" pageNumber="224" value="1959-03-01" valueMax="1959-03-20" valueMin="1959-03-01">
<collectingDate box="[516,666,260,285]" pageId="23" pageNumber="224" value="1959-03-01" valueMax="1959-03-20" valueMin="1959-03-01">1–20.iii.1959</collectingDate>
</date>
by Edwin Lindner. In the key to species provided to the three then known African 
<taxonomicName box="[326,516,295,320]" class="Insecta" family="Lonchaeidae" genus="Lamprolonchaea" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="23" pageNumber="224" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[326,516,295,320]" italics="true" pageId="23" pageNumber="224">Lamprolonchaea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
species (
<bibRefCitation author="Morge" box="[620,766,296,320]" pageId="23" pageNumber="224" refString="Morge, G. (1980) Lonchaeidae (Diptera) aus Afrika sudlich der Sahara mit Beschreibung von drei neuen Arten. Beitrage zur Entomologie, 30, 315 - 332." type="journal article" year="1980">Morge, 1980</bibRefCitation>
) 
<taxonomicName box="[781,869,297,320]" class="Insecta" family="Lonchaeidae" genus="Lamprolonchaea" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="23" pageNumber="224" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="ponti">
<emphasis box="[781,869,297,320]" italics="true" pageId="23" pageNumber="224">L. ponti</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is keyed out as having “ Arista deutlich gefiedert” (arista significantly feathery). On the basis of the short plumose arista this species is also assigned to the genus 
<taxonomicName box="[151,252,367,392]" class="Insecta" family="Lonchaeidae" genus="Fulgenta" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="23" pageNumber="205" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus" status="gen. nov.">
<emphasis box="[151,252,367,392]" italics="true" pageId="23" pageNumber="224">Fulgenta</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
</materialsCitation>
</paragraph>
